snippet.title: Hummingz - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Up for some retro arcade action spiced with extra bullets and BOSS enemies? Shoot your way through many different levels filled with nasty bugs, spiders, frogs, bees and more. Fight huge BOSS enemies and collect extras and play bonus waves. Retro Arcade action at its best!

Developed by Stefan Preuss
Also released on Evercade VS (...if you know how to access it)
